Package org.ivoa.dm.caom2.caom2.wcs

Class CoordAxis2D

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.caom2.caom2.wcs.CoordAxis2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="caom2:caom2.wcs.CoordAxis2D", role=dataType) public class CoordAxis2D extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
a two-dimensional coordinate axis pair: quantity, values, errors; it is usually only necessary to specify one of the range, bounds, or function as they describe the world and pixel coordinate coverage at different levels of detail and the less detailed description is redundant (exception: when the range or bounds and function are both specified, the range/bounds is a subset of the pixels described by the function and denotes the valid pixels. dataType: CoordAxis2D
